substep.action:
Parse the wt merge output for:
- Commit SHA on target after merge   → {{merged_commit}}
- Files changed count                → {{files_changed}}
- Insertions count                   → {{insertions}}
- Deletions count                    → {{deletions}}

wt merge prints these in a structured format (e.g., "auth.rs |
51 +++..., 2 files changed, +53"). Extract via simple regex on
the merge output.
